# Cloudflare Pages security headers — Kanbantt.
# Copied to the build output as /_headers via Vite's publicDir passthrough.
#
# CSP posture (Connection plan, part 4): a strict blast door at the script layer,
# an open door for BYO MCP spines at the connect layer. Composed from evidence in
# the built bundle + source, not assumption.
#   - script-src 'self' ONLY. No 'unsafe-inline', no 'unsafe-eval'. The built HTML
#     carries no inline <script>, and the bundle has no eval()/new Function()/wasm/
#     Worker (verified). OAuth is a top-level redirect — no GIS script is injected —
#     so nothing needs a script exception. This is the blast door.
#   - connect-src stays wide (https:) so a user's own MCP spine on ANY https origin
#     connects without a policy change (BYO spine). It ALSO allows http://localhost:*
#     and http://127.0.0.1:* — a deliberate, FLAGGED widening: Chrome exempts
#     localhost from mixed-content, so a deployed page can reach a loopback (PNA)
#     spine and the local preview harness can exercise a real connect. This added
#     permissiveness points only at the user's own machine.
#   - style-src keeps 'unsafe-inline' (React inline styles) + fonts.googleapis.com
#     (the runtime-injected Google Fonts stylesheet); font-src adds fonts.gstatic.com
#     (where that stylesheet's @font-face files live).
#   - Google OAuth: accounts.google.com is reached by NAVIGATION (window.location),
#     not script/xhr/frame, so it needs no directive; the token-exchange is a
#     same-origin Function, and revoke/userinfo/Drive/Calendar fetches ride https:.
#     The former GIS iframe (frame-src accounts.google.com) and GIS script origins
#     went away with the popup flow and are intentionally NOT present.
#   - Profile picture is not rendered (name + email only), so img-src carries no
#     googleusercontent origin — dead in the prior policy.

/*
  Content-Security-Policy: default-src 'self'; script-src 'self'; connect-src 'self' https: http://localhost:* http://127.0.0.1:*; style-src 'self' 'unsafe-inline' https://fonts.googleapis.com; img-src 'self' data: blob:; font-src 'self' https://fonts.gstatic.com data:; object-src 'none'; base-uri 'self'; form-action 'self'; frame-ancestors 'none'
  X-Content-Type-Options: nosniff
  Referrer-Policy: strict-origin-when-cross-origin
  X-Frame-Options: DENY
  Cross-Origin-Opener-Policy: same-origin
  Permissions-Policy: camera=(), microphone=(), geolocation=(), interest-cohort=()
  Strict-Transport-Security: max-age=63072000; includeSubDomains; preload
